{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01TUNywovdyvXmPYu6sMZp4b","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Phase 1–3 執行細節\n2\t\n3\t---\n4\t\n5\t## PHASE 1 — SECTOR ROTATION SCAN\n6\t\n7\t**Agent**: Sector Rotation Analyst\n8\t**資料來源**: `sector-analyst` CSV（不需 API key）\n9\t\n10\t> Phase 1 完成後，將各產業 `uptrend_ratio` 的平均值回填至 `_phase0.uptrend_ratio_overall`。\n11\t\n12\t**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 1\n13\t\n14\t---\n15\t\n16\t## PHASE 2 — THEME INTELLIGENCE\n17\t\n18\t**Agent**: Theme Intelligence Analyst\n19\t\n20\t**執行前 Cache Check**（FRESH = mtime < 3 小時前 / 10800s）：\n21\t1. 取 `skills/theme-detector/cache/theme_detector_*.json` 最新檔\n22\t   - **FRESH** → 直接載入，`theme_source: THEME_CACHE`，跳過 skill 執行，前往輸出 JSON\n23\t   - **STALE 或缺失** → 執行 `theme-detector` skill（FINVIZ Elite 優先，公開模式備用）\n24\t     - JSON cache → `skills/theme-detector/cache/`\n25\t     - MD 報告 → `reports/YYYYMMDD_theme_detector_HHMMSS.md`\n26\t\n27\t> Phase 2 與 Phase 3 完全獨立，可**並行執行**（節省 ~20 秒）\n28\t\n29\t**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 2\n30\t\n31\t---\n32\t\n33\t## PHASE 3 — NEWS CATALYST REVIEW\n34\t\n35\t**Agent**: News Catalyst Analyst\n36\t**資料來源**: `market-news-analyst` / `economic-calendar-fetcher` / `market-sentiment-analyzer`\n37\t\n38\t### ⚠️ Phase 3 強制執行規則（每次都跑，不可快取跳過）\n39\t\n40\t1. `market-sentiment-analyzer` skill — 取得即時情緒數值\n41\t2. `market-news-analyst` skill — 取得近 10 天新聞（**禁止用訓練資料舊新聞**）\n42\t3. `top_catalysts` 最少 5 筆，全部來自 skill WebSearch 結果\n43\t\n44\t### 情緒數值提取（填入 `political_overlay`）\n45\t\n46\t從 `market-sentiment-analyzer` 輸出提取：\n47\t- `composite_score` → `fear_greed_index`\n48\t- `composite_score label` → `fear_greed_label`\n49\t- `vix.current` → `vix_current`\n50\t- `put_call_ratio.equity_pc_ratio` → `put_call_ratio`\n51\t- `spy_momentum.rsi_14` → `spy_rsi`\n52\t\n53\t**extreme_sentiment 判斷**：`composite_score > 80 OR composite_score < 20` → `extreme_sentiment_triggered = true`\n54\t\n55\t---\n56\t\n57\t## Extreme Sentiment Playbook\n58\t\n59\t> 當 `extreme_sentiment_triggered = true` 時的級聯效應，依 Greed / Fear 分兩案處理。\n60\t\n61\t### Case 1: Extreme Greed（composite_score > 80）\n62\t\n63\t```\n64\tTrigger 條件：\n65\t  composite_score > 80\n66\t  OR (VIX < 15 AND Put/Call < 0.6 AND SPY RSI > 70)\n67\t\n68\t級聯動作：\n69\t  1. 所有 HOT 產業 → risk_flags += \"extreme_greed_warning\"\n70\t\n71\t  2. Phase 4b Devil's Advocate 義務：\n72\t     → 必須對至少 2 個 HOT 板塊提出「獲利了結/泡沫破裂」反方論點\n73\t     → tail-risk-analyzer 優先覆蓋前 3 個 HOT（效率上限不變，維持前 3）\n74\t\n75\t  3. Phase 4c 強制：\n76\t     → HOT 板塊 composite_score < 80 → 降為 WARM\n77\t     → final_regime_stance 不得為 AGGRESSIVE，最高 NEUTRAL\n78\t\n79\t  4. HANDOFF：明確提及「極度樂觀環境，謹慎進場」\n80\t```\n81\t\n82\t### Case 2: Extreme Fear（composite_score < 20）\n83\t\n84\t```\n85\tTrigger 條件：\n86\t  composite_score < 20\n87\t  OR (VIX > 30 AND Put/Call > 1.2 AND SPY RSI < 30)\n88\t\n89\t級聯動作：\n90\t  1. COLD/AVOID 產業：評估升級機會\n91\t     IF (COLD AND uptrend_ratio > 0.5 AND tail_risk < 40)\n92\t       → 標記 \"fear_capitulation_opportunity\"\n93\t\n94\t  2. Phase 4c：cyclical COLD 板塊 composite_score × 1.10\n95\t     （前提：基本面未惡化）\n96\t\n97\t  3. Devil's Advocate 義務軟化：\n98\t     → 不必強制挑戰 COLD 板塊\n99\t     → 改為尋找「恐慌被過度反應」的機會板塊\n100\t\n101\t  4. Phase 4c：可升級 final_regime_stance 為 AGGRESSIVE\n102\t     （條件：FTD 確認 + synthesized_exposure > 50%）\n103\t\n104\t  5. HANDOFF：提及「極度恐慌環境，高風險但機會浮現」\n105\t```\n106\t\n107\t---\n108\t\n109\t### Phase 3 執行清單\n110\t\n111\t- `market-sentiment-analyzer` skill（取代 web search: CNN Fear & Greed）\n112\t- `market-news-analyst`（10 天內市場新聞）\n113\t- `economic-calendar-fetcher` 或 web search: \"upcoming FOMC CPI NFP dates\"\n114\t- Web search: \"Trump tariff statement today\" / \"Trump Truth Social market\"\n115\t- Web search: \"sector named threat Trump today\"（若有政治事件）\n116\t\n117\t**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 3\n118\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"4b3daf5c-941d-4d5f-9002-88001fb41ffc","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:34:04.114Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/kavi/Documents/Claude/Projects/AI投資委員會/sector/phase_1-2-3.md","content":"# Phase 1–3 執行細節\n\n---\n\n## PHASE 1 — SECTOR ROTATION SCAN\n\n**Agent**: Sector Rotation Analyst\n**資料來源**: `sector-analyst` CSV（不需 API key）\n\n> Phase 1 完成後，將各產業 `uptrend_ratio` 的平均值回填至 `_phase0.uptrend_ratio_overall`。\n\n**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 1\n\n---\n\n## PHASE 2 — THEME INTELLIGENCE\n\n**Agent**: Theme Intelligence Analyst\n\n**執行前 Cache Check**（FRESH = mtime < 3 小時前 / 10800s）：\n1. 取 `skills/theme-detector/cache/theme_detector_*.json` 最新檔\n   - **FRESH** → 直接載入，`theme_source: THEME_CACHE`，跳過 skill 執行，前往輸出 JSON\n   - **STALE 或缺失** → 執行 `theme-detector` skill（FINVIZ Elite 優先，公開模式備用）\n     - JSON cache → `skills/theme-detector/cache/`\n     - MD 報告 → `reports/YYYYMMDD_theme_detector_HHMMSS.md`\n\n> Phase 2 與 Phase 3 完全獨立，可**並行執行**（節省 ~20 秒）\n\n**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 2\n\n---\n\n## PHASE 3 — NEWS CATALYST REVIEW\n\n**Agent**: News Catalyst Analyst\n**資料來源**: `market-news-analyst` / `economic-calendar-fetcher` / `market-sentiment-analyzer`\n\n### ⚠️ Phase 3 強制執行規則（每次都跑，不可快取跳過）\n\n1. `market-sentiment-analyzer` skill — 取得即時情緒數值\n2. `market-news-analyst` skill — 取得近 10 天新聞（**禁止用訓練資料舊新聞**）\n3. `top_catalysts` 最少 5 筆，全部來自 skill WebSearch 結果\n\n### 情緒數值提取（填入 `political_overlay`）\n\n從 `market-sentiment-analyzer` 輸出提取：\n- `composite_score` → `fear_greed_index`\n- `composite_score label` → `fear_greed_label`\n- `vix.current` → `vix_current`\n- `put_call_ratio.equity_pc_ratio` → `put_call_ratio`\n- `spy_momentum.rsi_14` → `spy_rsi`\n\n**extreme_sentiment 判斷**：`composite_score > 80 OR composite_score < 20` → `extreme_sentiment_triggered = true`\n\n---\n\n## Extreme Sentiment Playbook\n\n> 當 `extreme_sentiment_triggered = true` 時的級聯效應，依 Greed / Fear 分兩案處理。\n\n### Case 1: Extreme Greed（composite_score > 80）\n\n```\nTrigger 條件：\n  composite_score > 80\n  OR (VIX < 15 AND Put/Call < 0.6 AND SPY RSI > 70)\n\n級聯動作：\n  1. 所有 HOT 產業 → risk_flags += \"extreme_greed_warning\"\n\n  2. Phase 4b Devil's Advocate 義務：\n     → 必須對至少 2 個 HOT 板塊提出「獲利了結/泡沫破裂」反方論點\n     → tail-risk-analyzer 優先覆蓋前 3 個 HOT（效率上限不變，維持前 3）\n\n  3. Phase 4c 強制：\n     → HOT 板塊 composite_score < 80 → 降為 WARM\n     → final_regime_stance 不得為 AGGRESSIVE，最高 NEUTRAL\n\n  4. HANDOFF：明確提及「極度樂觀環境，謹慎進場」\n```\n\n### Case 2: Extreme Fear（composite_score < 20）\n\n```\nTrigger 條件：\n  composite_score < 20\n  OR (VIX > 30 AND Put/Call > 1.2 AND SPY RSI < 30)\n\n級聯動作：\n  1. COLD/AVOID 產業：評估升級機會\n     IF (COLD AND uptrend_ratio > 0.5 AND tail_risk < 40)\n       → 標記 \"fear_capitulation_opportunity\"\n\n  2. Phase 4c：cyclical COLD 板塊 composite_score × 1.10\n     （前提：基本面未惡化）\n\n  3. Devil's Advocate 義務軟化：\n     → 不必強制挑戰 COLD 板塊\n     → 改為尋找「恐慌被過度反應」的機會板塊\n\n  4. Phase 4c：可升級 final_regime_stance 為 AGGRESSIVE\n     （條件：FTD 確認 + synthesized_exposure > 50%）\n\n  5. HANDOFF：提及「極度恐慌環境，高風險但機會浮現」\n```\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3 執行清單\n\n- `market-sentiment-analyzer` skill（取代 web search: CNN Fear & Greed）\n- `market-news-analyst`（10 天內市場新聞）\n- `economic-calendar-fetcher` 或 web search: \"upcoming FOMC CPI NFP dates\"\n- Web search: \"Trump tariff statement today\" / \"Trump Truth Social market\"\n- Web search: \"sector named threat Trump today\"（若有政治事件）\n\n**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 3\n","numLines":118,"startLine":1,"totalLines":118}}}
