{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01YAYuLuB5kcjD33dWqUh8qE","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","name":"Agent","input":{"description":"Phase 3: News + Sentiment","prompt":"You are the News Catalyst Analyst for a pre-market sector intelligence protocol (date: 2026-04-16). Your job is to gather real-time market news and sentiment data.\n\nTasks:\n1. Run the market-sentiment-analyzer: use WebSearch to find current VIX level, Fear & Greed index, put/call ratio, and SPY RSI. Search for:\n   - \"VIX index today April 2026\"\n   - \"CNN Fear and Greed index today\"\n   - \"CBOE put call ratio today\"\n   - \"SPY RSI 14 today\"\n\n2. Run market-news-analyst: use WebSearch to find the most impactful market news from the past 3-5 days. Search for:\n   - \"US stock market news today April 16 2026\"\n   - \"FOMC Fed rate decision April 2026\"\n   - \"Trump tariff news today April 2026\"\n   - \"earnings season April 2026 results\"\n   - \"upcoming economic calendar this week April 2026\"\n\n3. Compile at least 5 top catalysts with impact assessment (positive/negative/neutral) and affected sectors.\n\n4. Determine:\n   - fear_greed_index (0-100)\n   - fear_greed_label (Extreme Fear / Fear / Neutral / Greed / Extreme Greed)\n   - vix_current\n   - put_call_ratio (if found)\n   - spy_rsi (if found)\n   - extreme_sentiment_triggered (true if fear_greed > 80 or < 20)\n   - market_regime (RISK_ON / RISK_OFF / VOLATILE)\n\n5. Look for any binary risk events within 48 hours that could impact specific sectors.\n\nReturn a structured summary with all findings.","model":"sonnet"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":2620,"cache_read_input_tokens":48043,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":2620},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","infere