{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016EDVuodVzFyX83gKbaY1fY","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"FOMC Fed rate decision April 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Top CD rates Tuesday, April 14, 2026: Lock in up to up to 4.20% | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/article/cd-rates-4-14-26/\"},{\"title\":\"Top CD rates Monday, April 13, 2026: Lock in up to up to 4.20% | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/article/cd-rates-4-13-26/\"},{\"title\":\"The Fed - Meeting calendars and information\",\"url\":\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/fomccalendars.htm\"},{\"title\":\"FedWatch - CME Group\",\"url\":\"https://www.cmegroup.com/markets/interest-rates/cme-fedwatch-tool.html\"},{\"title\":\"Federal Reserve Board - Federal Reserve issues FOMC statement\",\"url\":\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/newsevents/pressreleases/monetary20260318a.htm\"},{\"title\":\"FOMC Minutes, January 27-28, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/fomcminutes20260128.htm\"},{\"title\":\"FOMC Minutes, March 17-18, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.federalreserve.gov/monetarypolicy/fomcminutes20260318.htm\"},{\"title\":\"United States Fed Funds Interest Rate\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/united-states/interest-rate\"},{\"title\":\"When is the next FOMC meeting? | Equals Money\",\"url\":\"https://equalsmoney.com/economic-calendar/events/fomc-meeting\"},{\"title\":\"FOMC Meeting – April 2026 | CalendarX\",\"url\":\"https://www.calendarx.com/events/fomc-meeting-april-2026\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what I found about the FOMC Fed rate decision for April 2026:\n\n## Upcoming April FOMC Meeting\n\nThe FOMC's next meeting is scheduled for April 28-29, 2026.\n\n## Current Fed Rate Status\n\nAt present, the federal funds rate is 3.50%-3.75%. At the most recent March 18, 2026 meeting, the Committee decided to maintain the target range for the federal funds rate at 3‑1/2 to 3‑3/4 percent.\n\n## Recent Context\n\nThe Federal Reserve cut its benchmark federal funds rate three times in 2025 and numerous banks responded by reducing their CD and savings interest rates. Looking ahead, policymakers still signaled one reduction in the fed funds rate this year and another in 2027, though the timing remains unclear.\n\nThe April meeting will provide the FOMC an opportunity to assess recent economic data and determine whether any adjustments to monetary policy are warranted.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"4e514389-6507-4318-b356-b051b54af642","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:34:52.468Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_011A7zyQR8WQS7MYu5Evwgjy","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"Trump tariff news today April 16 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Tariff Tracker: 2026 Trump Tariffs & Trade War by the Numbers\",\"url\":\"https://taxfoundation.org/research/all/federal/trump-tariffs-trade-war/\"},{\"title\":\"TPC Tariff Tracker\",\"url\":\"https://taxpolicycenter.org/features/tracking-trump-tariffs\"},{\"title\":\"Trump threatens 50% tariffs on China as report suggests plans for arms shipment to Iran\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/13/trump-threatens-50percent-tariffs-on-china-as-report-suggests-plans-for-arms-shipment-to-iran.html\"},{\"title\":\"Tariffs in the second Trump administration - Wikipedia\",\"url\":\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tariffs_in_the_second_Trump_administration\"},{\"title\":\"Fact Sheet: President Donald J. Trump Strengthens Tariffs on Steel, Aluminum, and Copper Imports – The White House\",\"url\":\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/fact-sheets/2026/04/fact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-strengthens-tariffs-on-steel-aluminum-and-copper-imports/\"},{\"title\":\"Trump’s tariffs dealt an economic blow to all 50 states, study finds | Fortune\",\"url\":\"https://fortune.com/2026/04/14/how-tariffs-dealt-economic-blow-in-all-50-states/\"},{\"title\":\"Trump tariff fallout: Some industries grapple with lingering effects one year later\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/03/trump-tariffs-trade-war-impact.html\"},{\"title\":\"The Trump administration’s new tariff road map | Grant Thornton\",\"url\":\"https://www.grantthornton.com/insights/alerts/tax/2026/insights/the-trump-administration-new-tariff-road-map\"},{\"title\":\"Presidential Tariff Actions | United States Trade Representative\",\"url\":\"https://ustr.gov/trade-topics/presidential-tariff-actions\"},{\"title\":\"Trump Tariff Rates Could Be Restored by Early July: Bessent - Bloomberg\",\"url\":\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/trump-tariff-rates-could-be-restored-by-early-july-bessent\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here are the latest Trump tariff news items from around April 16, 2026:\n\n## Recent Tariff Developments\n\n**China Tariff Threat**: President Trump threatened to impose a 50% tariff on China after a report emerged that Beijing was preparing to deliver a shipment of new air defense systems to Iran.\n\n**Tariff Restoration Plans**: Treasury Secretary Scott Bessent said the Trump administration could restore tariffs to previous levels by early July through Section 301 studies.\n\n**Investigation Deadlines**: Public comments for manufacturing-related and forced labor-related investigations are due April 16.\n\n## Broader 2026 Tariff Context\n\nThe Trump tariffs are the largest US tax increase as a percent of GDP since 1993 and amount to an average tax increase per US household of $1,500 in 2026.\n\nBy 2026, U.S. businesses and consumers were covering almost 90% of tariff costs, according to Federal Reserve research.\n\nPresident Trump announced two sets of tariffs under Section 232 of the Trade Expansion Act on April 2, 2026 - the first restructures and reduces tariffs on steel, aluminum, and copper, while the second imposes tariffs of up to 100 percent on patented pharmaceutical imports.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"79cb0886-f717-4b7b-ac61-cc252aa59155","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:34:52.835Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_0163nmCCpoX3K86aDGsD96vp","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"earnings season April 2026 results tech banks\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Company Earnings Calendar - Yahoo Finance\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/calendar/earnings/\"},{\"title\":\"FinancialContent - Wall Street’s New Benchmark: Morgan Stanley Shatters Records with Q1 2026 Performance\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/marketminute-2026-4-15-wall-streets-new-benchmark-morgan-stanley-shatters-records-with-q1-2026-performance\"},{\"title\":\"Breakfast News: Big Banks Launch Earnings Season | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/breakfast-news/2026/04/13/breakfast-news-big-banks-launch-earnings-season/\"},{\"title\":\"US Q1 Earnings 2026 Begin: S&P 500 Profit Growth Seen at 12.5% as Banks, Big Tech Set the Tone\",\"url\":\"https://internationalnewsandviews.com/us-q1-2026-earnings-sp500-growth-banks-results-outlook-401326-2/\"},{\"title\":\"Q1 Earnings Season Begins This Week. Here's What to Expect. | The Motley Fool\",\"url\":\"https://www.fool.com/investing/2026/04/14/q1-earnings-season-begins-what-to-expect/\"},{\"title\":\"Citigroup (C) earnings 1Q 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/14/citigroup-c-earnings-1q-2026.html\"},{\"title\":\"Earnings Season 2026: Banks, Geopolitics & Market Outlook\",\"url\":\"https://markets.vontobel.com/en-fi/inspiration/128191/earnings-season-begins-banks-on-the-front-lines-and-the-shadow-of-geopolitics\"},{\"title\":\"FinancialContent - JPMorgan Chase Defies Economic Headwinds with Blockbuster Q1 2026 Results\",\"url\":\"https://markets.financialcontent.com/stocks/article/marketminute-2026-4-14-jpmorgan-chase-defies-economic-headwinds-with-blockbuster-q1-2026-results\"},{\"title\":\"Q1 2026 Earnings Preview: Double-Digit Growth and the Visibility Gap | Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/analysis/q1-2026-earnings-preview-doubledigit-growth-and-the-visibility-gap-200678418\"},{\"title\":\"Earnings Calendar - Investing.com\",\"url\":\"https://www.investing.com/earnings-calendar\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what's happening with earnings season in April 2026:\n\n## Overall Earnings Expectations\n\nS&P 500 earnings are expected to grow approximately 12.5% year-over-year, marking the sixth consecutive quarter of double-digit expansion. Some sources project even stronger growth, with S&P 500 earnings growth for Q1 potentially reaching as much as 19%, which would be the highest growth rate in more than four years.\n\n## Bank Earnings Results\n\nSeveral major banks have already reported strong Q1 2026 results:\n\n**JPMorgan Chase:** The bank reported $16.5 billion in net income, up sharply from $14.6 billion in the same period last year. The 13% profit increase and surge in investment banking fees suggest that the \"deal-making drought\" of previous years has officially ended.\n\n**Morgan Stanley:** The Investment Banking division saw revenue jump 36% year-over-year, primarily fueled by a massive wave of M&A activity that began in mid-2025.\n\n**Citigroup:** The firm beat on both top and bottom lines, reporting earnings per share of $3.06 versus a $2.65 estimate and revenue of $24.63 billion versus a $23.55 billion estimate, marking its best quarterly revenue in a decade.\n\n## Sector Outlook\n\nInformation Technology (45.0%), Materials (24.2%), and Financials (15.1%) are leading the earnings growth pack. Demand for agentic AI has climbed so high it's leading to chip shortages, which should be good news for revenue at major semiconductor companies.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"f544af04-5a07-4bc5-a96c-874bb4b1130c","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:34:55.341Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WQks6y3Lk5F3EfQ9NB9r6R","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"US stock market news today April 16 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Stock market news for April 14, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/13/stock-markets-today-live-updates.html\"},{\"title\":\"Stock market today: Dow, S&P 500, Nasdaq edge higher as Trump says Iran wants to talk, US blockades Hormuz\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/live/stock-market-today-dow-sp-500-nasdaq-mixed-after-trump-orders-hormuz-blockade-against-iran-145712025.html\"},{\"title\":\"Stock Market Today: Dow, S&P Live Updates for April 15 - Bloomberg\",\"url\":\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates\"},{\"title\":\"Stock Market Today: Dow, S&P Live Updates for April 14 - Bloomberg\",\"url\":\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates\"},{\"title\":\"Stock market news for April 13, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/12/stock-market-today-live-updates.html\"},{\"title\":\"Stock market news for April 2, 2026\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/01/stock-market-today-live-updates.html\"},{\"title\":\"Stock market today: S&P 500, Nasdaq rally toward record highs, oil tumbles as Iran deal optimism grows\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/article/stock-market-today-dow-sp-500-nasdaq-rise-amid-iran-deal-hopes-earnings-rush-225637251.html\"},{\"title\":\"Stock market today: Live updates\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/14/stock-market-today-live-updates.html\"},{\"title\":\"Yahoo Finance - Stock Market Live, Quotes, Business & Finance News\",\"url\":\"https://finance.yahoo.com/\"},{\"title\":\"Stock Market Today (Apr. 14, 2026): Nasdaq rises nearly 2% despite bad wholesale inflation print, Iran War uncertainty - TheStreet\",\"url\":\"https://www.thestreet.com/latest-news/stock-market-today-apr-14-2026-updates\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's the latest US stock market news. Note that the search found recent reporting through April 15, 2026 (today), but no specific news for April 16:\n\n## Latest Market Updates\n\nUS stocks are holding firm near an all-time high following a rally powered by optimism around a potential peace deal in the Middle East, with traders now eyeing confirmation of new talks.\n\n### Recent Performance\n\nThe S&P 500 gained 1.18% and closed at 6,967.38, the Dow Jones Industrial Average added 317.74 points, or 0.66%, to close at 48,535.99, and the Nasdaq Composite advanced 1.96% and ended at 23,639.08. The tech-heavy Nasdaq 100 rose 1.8% for a 10th straight day of gains — its longest such streak since 2021.\n\n### Key Drivers\n\nThe S&P 500 Index is closing within sight of a fresh record as optimism on the possibility of further peace talks between the US and Iran has pushed down oil prices.\n\n### Earnings Season\n\nJPMorgan Chase beat Wall Street's first-quarter expectations, with a 13% year-over-year profit increase to $16.5 billion, or $5.94 per share, and $49.8 billion in revenue, up 10% from a year ago.\n\nThe search results don't contain specific news for April 16, 2026, as that date may be in the future relative to when these articles were published.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"d875de03-8b70-443e-a7cc-37413abea7ad","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:34:55.671Z"}
