{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CqNkL8sraXGDzWPRGptaGX","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"oil price crude WTI today April 16 2026 Iran ceasefire\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Crude Oil - Price - Chart - Historical Data - News\",\"url\":\"https://tradingeconomics.com/commodity/crude-oil\"},{\"title\":\"Oil rally loses steam after Israel agrees to negotiate with Lebanon\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/09/oil-prices-today-wti-brent-iran-accuse-us-of-ceasefire-breach.html\"},{\"title\":\"Oil plunges, Dow sees its best day in a year after US-Iran ceasefire, but ‘hurdles remain’ | CNN Business\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnn.com/2026/04/07/markets/us-stocks-oil-trump-iran-ceasefire\"},{\"title\":\"US-Iran, two-week ceasefire: gas and oil prices drop Materia Rinnovabile | Renewable Matter\",\"url\":\"https://www.renewablematter.eu/en/us-iran-ceasefire\"},{\"title\":\"US-Iran Ceasefire Impact on Oil Prices & Stock Market 2026\",\"url\":\"https://intellectia.ai/blog/us-iran-ceasefire-oil-prices-stock-market-impact-2026\"},{\"title\":\"Iran ceasefire effect: Oil plunges as European markets surge | Euronews\",\"url\":\"https://www.euronews.com/business/2026/04/08/iran-ceasefire-pushes-oil-prices-down-as-markets-remain-cautious\"},{\"title\":\"Oil plunges on Iran ceasefire news, setting the stage for some relief on gas prices\",\"url\":\"https://www.nbcnews.com/business/markets/iran-war-ceasefire-oil-prices-stocks-trump-rcna267229\"},{\"title\":\"U.S. oil price tumbles below $92 as White House considers further talks with Iran\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/14/oil-wti-brent-as-markets-hormuz-blockade-vance-trump.html\"},{\"title\":\"U.S. crude oil posts biggest one-day drop since 2020 on U.S.-Iran ceasefire agreement\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/07/oil-prices-iran-war-trump-deadline-strait-hormuz.html\"},{\"title\":\"Oil prices surge on Trump's blockade vow, failed U.S.-Iran talks\",\"url\":\"https://www.axios.com/2026/04/12/oil-prices-surge-trump-iran-blockade\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's the latest information on WTI crude oil prices and the Iran ceasefire situation as of April 16, 2026:\n\n## Current Oil Price\n\nWTI crude futures traded around $93 per barrel on Wednesday, holding losses from the previous session as investors anticipated a second round of peace negotiations between the US and Iran before the two-week ceasefire lapses.\n\n## Ceasefire and Negotiations\n\nPresident Donald Trump reportedly indicated talks could restart \"within the next two days\" in Pakistan after last weekend's discussions broke down. Negotiators aim to hold further discussions before the ceasefire expires next week.\n\n## Key Factors Affecting Oil Prices\n\nThe US continues to enforce a naval blockade on Iranian oil exports through the Strait of Hormuz, while Tehran is weighing a temporary halt in shipments via the corridor to support progress toward a deal.\n\nThe IEA expects global oil demand to decline this year for the first time since the 2020 pandemic, as elevated prices curb consumption.\n\nThe situation remains volatile with significant uncertainty surrounding whether the ceasefire will hold and whether the critical Strait of Hormuz will fully reopen for oil shipments.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"af2d9b6b-9c01-4fbf-b140-c9379bc58bd2","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:35:14.736Z"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DFWimGfezzSBSp11n98jX3","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"pharmaceuticals tariff 100% Trump April 2026 biotech sector impact\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Pharma tariffs force biotech to weigh price deals\",\"url\":\"https://www.axios.com/2026/04/13/pharma-tariffs-trump-pressure-biotech-deals\"},{\"title\":\"Trump follows through with 100% tariff threat on some imported drugs | STAT\",\"url\":\"https://www.statnews.com/2026/04/02/trump-pharma-tariffs-100-percent-on-some-imported-drugs-exemptions/\"},{\"title\":\"Trump's 100% pharma tariff: What it means for prices\",\"url\":\"https://www.advisory.com/daily-briefing/2026/04/06/pharmaceutical-tariffs\"},{\"title\":\"Trump revives pharma tariffs with 100% charges, but leaves loopholes | BioPharma Dive\",\"url\":\"https://www.biopharmadive.com/news/trump-revives-pharma-tariffs-100-percent-levies/816584/\"},{\"title\":\"Trump prepares pharmaceutical tariffs of up to 100%\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/02/trump-pharmaceutical-tariffs-100percent.html\"},{\"title\":\"Trump’s 100% pharma tariffs will have a limited effect on the sector | articles | ING THINK\",\"url\":\"https://think.ing.com/articles/100-pharma-tariffs-will-have-a-limited-effect-on-the-sector/\"},{\"title\":\"Fact Sheet: President Donald J. Trump Bolsters National Security and Strengthens U.S. Supply Chains by Imposing Tariffs on Patented Pharmaceutical Products – The White House\",\"url\":\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/fact-sheets/2026/04/fact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-bolsters-national-security-and-strengthens-u-s-supply-chains-by-imposing-tariffs-on-patented-pharmaceutical-products/\"},{\"title\":\"100% On Brand: U.S. Imposes New Tariffs (and Key Exemptions) on Patented Pharmaceuticals | Insights | Ropes & Gray LLP\",\"url\":\"https://www.ropesgray.com/en/insights/alerts/2026/04/100-on-brand-us-imposes-new-tariffs-and-key-exemptions-on-patented-pharmaceuticals\"},{\"title\":\"Trump policies, China's biotech boom are ending Europe's pharma powerhouse era\",\"url\":\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/04/11/trump-pharma-tariffs-mfn-china-europe-biotech-stocks.html\"},{\"title\":\"Trump eyes 100% tariff rate for companies that have not struck MFN deals: Bloomberg\",\"url\":\"https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/trump-set-impose-100-tariff-drugs-companies-have-not-struck-mfn-deals\"}]\n\nBased on the search results, here's what the 100% pharmaceutical tariff announced by Trump in April 2026 means for the biotech sector:\n\n## Overview\n\nOn April 2, 2026, President Trump announced 100% tariffs on patented pharmaceutical products and key inputs, marking one of the most aggressive trade actions affecting the life sciences sector.\n\n## Rationale and Goals\n\nThe Trump administration argues the tariffs are needed to spur domestic pharmaceutical manufacturing and address what's become a national security issue, with China rapidly building its life sciences capabilities. There are already $400 billion in commitments to reshore manufacturing so far in the sector during Trump's term.\n\n## Impact on Biotech Sector\n\nThe impact is mixed and depends heavily on company size and deals:\n\n**Small and Mid-Size Companies:** 100% tariffs on patented pharmaceuticals and active ingredients could be devastating for some of the small and midsize biotech companies that develop more than half of all Food and Drug Administration‑approved medicines. Smaller companies pursuing large indications may be most vulnerable, but overall given high margins, potential carve-outs, and time to adjust, the overall threat to the sector should be low.\n\n**Overall Assessment:** The tariff is geopolitical in nature and should be seen as a shot across the bow for more intense competition between the US and China in biotech and pharma.\n\n## Exemptions and Relief\n\nCompanies have several pathways to reduce or eliminate tariffs:\n\n- For companies that reached MFN pricing deals—including 13 companies—the duty rate is 0% rather than 100%, though the 0% rate will expire as of January 20, 2029.\n- For companies that enter into onshoring commitments, the duty rate is 20% rather than 100%, though the rate will rise to 100% in four years (i.e., in 2030).\n- If a pharmaceutical product is from the European Union, Japan, Korea, or Switzerland and Liechtenstein, a 15% tariff will apply.\n\n## Timeline\n\nThe tariffs will come into effect in 120 days for certain large companies, and 180 days for smaller companies.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01CrdDqZAnkXDo5ue5gK22ZN","session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"972799d5-84a9-44fc-854c-8b9ba1111889","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:35:17.800Z"}
