{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01W9fUQr8aLbQZ6f6FiF91T4","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# Phase 4–5 執行細節\n2\t\n3\t---\n4\t\n5\t## PHASE 4 — MULTI-AGENT DEBATE\n6\t\n7\t**Agent**: Portfolio Strategist (PS) 主持，各 Agent 輪流發言\n8\t\n9\t---\n10\t\n11\t### Step 1 (Phase 4a) — 各 Agent 提案\n12\t\n13\t三個 Agent（Sector Rotation / Theme Intelligence / News Catalyst）同時提案，PS 合成。\n14\t可**並行執行**，最後由 PS 整合。\n15\t\n16\t**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 4a\n17\t\n18\t---\n19\t\n20\t### Step 2 (Phase 4b) — Devil's Advocate\n21\t\n22\t#### consensus_warning 精確定義\n23\t\n24\t```\n25\tconsensus_warning = true  IF 某板塊同時滿足所有三個條件：\n26\t  ✓ Phase 1: rotation_signal = INFLOW\n27\t  ✓ Phase 2: lifecycle_stage ∈ [Accelerating, Trending]\n28\t  ✓ Phase 3: sector_news_sentiment = bullish\n29\t\n30\t  表示：輪動、主題熱度、新聞催化三者全看多，無任何分歧。\n31\t\n32\tDA 義務規則：\n33\t  IF consensus_warning = true:\n34\t    → MUST 提交 challenge_targets（不可省略）\n35\t    → counter_evidence ≥ 2 句（含具體數據或邏輯）\n36\t    → 若無實質論點 → 標記 \"FORCED_CHALLENGE_WEAK\"（低信度）\n37\t\n38\t  IF consensus_warning = false:\n39\t    → 優先挑戰 tail_risk_score 最高的 2-3 個板塊\n40\t```\n41\t\n42\t#### Tail Risk 觸發規則\n43\t\n44\t> **效率上限**：HOT 產業 > 3 個 → 僅對 `composite_score` 前 3 名執行 `tail-risk-analyzer`，其餘標記 `SKIPPED_CAPACITY_LIMIT`。\n45\t\n46\t```\n47\t對每個納入檢查的 HOT 產業（composite_score > 75）的 proxy_etf：\n48\t→ 執行 tail-risk-analyzer skill（per-stock mode，傳入 proxy_etf ticker）\n49\t→ fragility_label = FRAGILE 或 EXTREMELY FRAGILE\n50\t  → 必須將此產業加入 challenge_targets\n51\t→ tail_risk_score > 70 OR excess_kurtosis > 5\n52\t  → risk_flags += \"fat_tail_warning\"\n53\t→ 2020 COVID 情境回測下跌 > 40%\n54\t  → risk_flags += \"crash_vulnerability\"\n55\t```\n56\t\n57\t**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 4b\n58\t\n59\t---\n60\t\n61\t### Step 3 (Phase 4c) — PS 仲裁決策樹\n62\t\n63\t```\n64\tPORTFOLIO STRATEGIST ARBITRATION DECISION TREE\n65\t═══════════════════════════════════════════════\n66\t\n67\tSTEP A — Signal Conflict Check\n68\t  IF signal_conflict = true:\n69\t    → final_regime_stance CANNOT be AGGRESSIVE\n70\t    → max allowed = NEUTRAL\n71\t\n72\tSTEP B — Exposure Floor Check\n73\t  IF synthesized_exposure < 40%:\n74\t    → MUST flag ≥ 3 sectors as AVOID（無例外）\n75\t\n76\tSTEP C — Cycle Adjustment\n77\t  IF cycle_phase ∈ [Late, Recession]:\n78\t    FOR EACH cyclical sector  → composite_score × 0.85\n79\t    FOR EACH defensive sector → composite_score × 1.10\n80\t\n81\tSTEP D — Tail Risk Downgrades\n82\t  IF fragility_label = EXTREMELY_FRAGILE:\n83\t    → DOWNGRADE: HOT → WARM（不調整分數，直接降 label）\n84\t    → risk_flags += \"fragility_downgrade\"\n85\t  ELIF (fragility_label = FRAGILE AND extreme_sentiment_triggered = true):\n86\t    → DOWNGRADE: HOT → WARM\n87\t    → risk_flags += \"extreme_sentiment_fragile_combo\"\n88\t\n89\tSTEP E — Binary Risk\n90\t  FOR EACH upcoming_binary_risk (timing = within_48h):\n91\t    FOR EACH affected_sector:\n92\t      → composite_score × 0.70\n93\t      → risk_flags += \"binary_risk_within_48h\"\n94\t\n95\tSTEP F — Consensus Safeguard\n96\t  IF (consensus_warning = true AND devils_advocate_accepted = []):\n97\t    → regime_confidence × 0.85\n98\t\n99\tSTEP G — Signal Conflict Safeguard\n100\t  IF (signal_conflict = true AND sector.verdict = HOT):\n101\t    → DOWNGRADE to WARM\n102\t\n103\tFINAL VERDICT ASSIGNMENT:\n104\t  score = adjusted composite_score（套用所有乘數後）\n105\t  score >= 75 → HOT（除非 STEP D 降級）\n106\t  50-74      → WARM\n107\t  25-49      → COLD\n108\t  < 25       → AVOID\n109\t  Cap: score ∈ [0, 100]\n110\t\n111\tFINAL REGIME STANCE:\n112\t  HOT >= 3 AND AVOID = 0 AND synthesized_exposure >= 60% → AGGRESSIVE\n113\t  HOT >= 1 AND median_verdict >= WARM                    → NEUTRAL\n114\t  COLD >= 3 OR synthesized_exposure < 40%                → DEFENSIVE\n115\t```\n116\t\n117\t**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 4c\n118\t\n119\t---\n120\t\n121\t## PHASE 5 — SECTOR VERDICT\n122\t\n123\t**Agent**: Portfolio Strategist (PS)\n124\t\n125\t完成後執行：\n126\t1. 寫入 `./sector_logs/YYYY-MM-DD_sector_intel.json`（供 bridge.py 和其他 protocol 讀取）\n127\t2. 將 FINAL VERDICT TABLE 存為 `../reports/YYYY-MM-DD_sector_report.md`\n128\t\n129\t> ⚠️ **JSON Schema 必須嚴格遵守**（見 `schema.md` Phase 5）：\n130\t> - `bridge.py` 依賴 `_phase0`、`_phase1`、`_phase3` 三個子物件，key 名稱不可更換\n131\t> - `protocol_version` 固定為 `\"V1.2\"`\n132\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"75e35f77-da22-4546-82cd-6252b544ace6","uuid":"3b020161-5c05-469d-9d03-769e0202be8e","timestamp":"2026-04-15T16:36:40.119Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/kavi/Documents/Claude/Projects/AI投資委員會/sector/phase_4-5.md","content":"# Phase 4–5 執行細節\n\n---\n\n## PHASE 4 — MULTI-AGENT DEBATE\n\n**Agent**: Portfolio Strategist (PS) 主持，各 Agent 輪流發言\n\n---\n\n### Step 1 (Phase 4a) — 各 Agent 提案\n\n三個 Agent（Sector Rotation / Theme Intelligence / News Catalyst）同時提案，PS 合成。\n可**並行執行**，最後由 PS 整合。\n\n**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 4a\n\n---\n\n### Step 2 (Phase 4b) — Devil's Advocate\n\n#### consensus_warning 精確定義\n\n```\nconsensus_warning = true  IF 某板塊同時滿足所有三個條件：\n  ✓ Phase 1: rotation_signal = INFLOW\n  ✓ Phase 2: lifecycle_stage ∈ [Accelerating, Trending]\n  ✓ Phase 3: sector_news_sentiment = bullish\n\n  表示：輪動、主題熱度、新聞催化三者全看多，無任何分歧。\n\nDA 義務規則：\n  IF consensus_warning = true:\n    → MUST 提交 challenge_targets（不可省略）\n    → counter_evidence ≥ 2 句（含具體數據或邏輯）\n    → 若無實質論點 → 標記 \"FORCED_CHALLENGE_WEAK\"（低信度）\n\n  IF consensus_warning = false:\n    → 優先挑戰 tail_risk_score 最高的 2-3 個板塊\n```\n\n#### Tail Risk 觸發規則\n\n> **效率上限**：HOT 產業 > 3 個 → 僅對 `composite_score` 前 3 名執行 `tail-risk-analyzer`，其餘標記 `SKIPPED_CAPACITY_LIMIT`。\n\n```\n對每個納入檢查的 HOT 產業（composite_score > 75）的 proxy_etf：\n→ 執行 tail-risk-analyzer skill（per-stock mode，傳入 proxy_etf ticker）\n→ fragility_label = FRAGILE 或 EXTREMELY FRAGILE\n  → 必須將此產業加入 challenge_targets\n→ tail_risk_score > 70 OR excess_kurtosis > 5\n  → risk_flags += \"fat_tail_warning\"\n→ 2020 COVID 情境回測下跌 > 40%\n  → risk_flags += \"crash_vulnerability\"\n```\n\n**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 4b\n\n---\n\n### Step 3 (Phase 4c) — PS 仲裁決策樹\n\n```\nPORTFOLIO STRATEGIST ARBITRATION DECISION TREE\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nSTEP A — Signal Conflict Check\n  IF signal_conflict = true:\n    → final_regime_stance CANNOT be AGGRESSIVE\n    → max allowed = NEUTRAL\n\nSTEP B — Exposure Floor Check\n  IF synthesized_exposure < 40%:\n    → MUST flag ≥ 3 sectors as AVOID（無例外）\n\nSTEP C — Cycle Adjustment\n  IF cycle_phase ∈ [Late, Recession]:\n    FOR EACH cyclical sector  → composite_score × 0.85\n    FOR EACH defensive sector → composite_score × 1.10\n\nSTEP D — Tail Risk Downgrades\n  IF fragility_label = EXTREMELY_FRAGILE:\n    → DOWNGRADE: HOT → WARM（不調整分數，直接降 label）\n    → risk_flags += \"fragility_downgrade\"\n  ELIF (fragility_label = FRAGILE AND extreme_sentiment_triggered = true):\n    → DOWNGRADE: HOT → WARM\n    → risk_flags += \"extreme_sentiment_fragile_combo\"\n\nSTEP E — Binary Risk\n  FOR EACH upcoming_binary_risk (timing = within_48h):\n    FOR EACH affected_sector:\n      → composite_score × 0.70\n      → risk_flags += \"binary_risk_within_48h\"\n\nSTEP F — Consensus Safeguard\n  IF (consensus_warning = true AND devils_advocate_accepted = []):\n    → regime_confidence × 0.85\n\nSTEP G — Signal Conflict Safeguard\n  IF (signal_conflict = true AND sector.verdict = HOT):\n    → DOWNGRADE to WARM\n\nFINAL VERDICT ASSIGNMENT:\n  score = adjusted composite_score（套用所有乘數後）\n  score >= 75 → HOT（除非 STEP D 降級）\n  50-74      → WARM\n  25-49      → COLD\n  < 25       → AVOID\n  Cap: score ∈ [0, 100]\n\nFINAL REGIME STANCE:\n  HOT >= 3 AND AVOID = 0 AND synthesized_exposure >= 60% → AGGRESSIVE\n  HOT >= 1 AND median_verdict >= WARM                    → NEUTRAL\n  COLD >= 3 OR synthesized_exposure < 40%                → DEFENSIVE\n```\n\n**JSON Schema** → 見 `schema.md` Phase 4c\n\n---\n\n## PHASE 5 — SECTOR VERDICT\n\n**Agent**: Portfolio Strategist (PS)\n\n完成後執行：\n1. 寫入 `./sector_logs/YYYY-MM-DD_sector_intel.json`（供 bridge.py 和其他 protocol 讀取）\n2. 將 FINAL VERDICT TABLE 存為 `../reports/YYYY-MM-DD_sector_report.md`\n\n> ⚠️ **JSON Schema 必須嚴格遵守**（見 `schema.md` Phase 5）：\n> - `bridge.py` 依賴 `_phase0`、`_phase1`、`_phase3` 三個子物件，key 名稱不可更換\n> - `protocol_version` 固定為 `\"V1.2\"`\n","numLines":132,"startLine":1,"totalLines":132}}}
